	(22, 6, 5, '2012-04-14', 'Gabriel', '<p>St. Jude Square is a neighborhood living in fear and despair. The dueling gangs of local kingpins Dash and Antuan terrorize the streets and the citizens live without a shred of hope&hellip; until mysterious stranger Ryan Hong (Cung Le) arrives in town. He begins to play one gang against the other using his unparalleled martial arts skills, and by calling on the teachings of his brilliant mentor Tiano (Jean-Claude Van Damme) to find the strength to battle back.</p>', 'DRAGON EYES', '<p>Tanggal Rilis : 11 Mei 2012<br />Jenis Film : Action | Crime | Drama<br />Diperankan Oleh : Jean-Claude Van Damme, Peter Weller and Cung Le</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Ringkasan Cerita FILM DRAGON EYES (2012) :</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>St. Jude Square is a neighborhood living in fear and despair. The dueling gangs of local kingpins Dash and Antuan terrorize the streets and the citizens live without a shred of hope&hellip; until mysterious stranger Ryan Hong (Cung Le) arrives in town. He begins to play one gang against the other using his unparalleled martial arts skills, and by calling on the teachings of his brilliant mentor Tiano (Jean-Claude Van Damme) to find the strength to battle back.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>However, just as he begins to bring the community under control, Hong is confronted by Mr. V, the town&rsquo;s ruthless and corrupt police chief. At first Mr. V is impressed by Hong&rsquo;s skill, but soon sees Hong as a threat to his regime, and the two warriors are locked in a head-to-head battle, pitting the fear and corruption of Mr. V&rsquo;s regime versus the new beginning Hong represents for the people of St. Jude Square.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Film tersebut bisa di download di : &nbsp;*</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>1.&nbsp;http://adf.ly/7PYgB</p>\n<p>2.&nbsp;http://adf.ly/7PYjh</p>\n<p>3.&nbsp;http://adf.ly/7PYlt</p>\n<p>4.&nbsp;http://adf.ly/7PYo3</p>', ''),
	(23, 7, 6, '2012-04-14', 'Purwo Hadi Kusumo', '<p>Guys, Akhirnya ID-SIRTII mengadakan kembali pelatihan "Cyber Security Training". Untuk Gelombang V. Pelatihan akan di adakan pada tanggal 23 - 24 April 2012.</p>', 'Digital Forensic Training', '<p>Guys, Akhirnya ID-SIRTII mengadakan kembali pelatihan "Cyber Security Training". Untuk Gelombang V. Pelatihan akan di adakan pada tanggal 23 - 24 April 2012.</p>\n<p><br />Pelatihan ini akan di adakan selama 2 hari . Berikut Jadwal pelatihannya :</p>\n<p><br />Hari 1</p>\n<p>Sesi 1 : &nbsp;09.00 &ndash; 12.00 &nbsp; &nbsp;Forensic OverviewSesi 2 : 13.00 s.d 16.00 &nbsp; File System Analysis</p>\n<p><br />Hari 2</p>\n<p>Sesi 1 : &nbsp;09.00 &ndash; 12.00 &nbsp; &nbsp;Media AnalysisSesi 2 : 13.00 s.d 16.00 &nbsp; Data Carving</p>\n<p><br />Untuk Pendaftarannya bisa di lakukan dengan meng-klik alamat : <a href="http://adf.ly/7PamT">http://adf.ly/7PamT</a></p>\n<p><br />(Pendaftaran paling lambat tanggal 20 April 2012. Tempat terbatas)</p>', ''),
	(24, 7, 6, '2012-04-14', 'Purwo Hadi Kusumo', '<p>Dapat informasi dari teman-teman di relawan TIK dalam rangka acara Munas, relawan TIK mengadakan acara dengan tema "Festival TIK Untuk Rakyat" yang akan di adakan pada tanggal 28-29 April 2012 di gedung politeknik Telkom Bandung.</p>', 'Festival TIK Untuk Rakyat', '<p>Dapat informasi dari teman-teman di relawan TIK dalam rangka acara Munas, relawan TIK mengadakan acara dengan tema "Festival TIK Untuk Rakyat" yang akan di adakan pada tanggal 28-29 April 2012 di gedung politeknik Telkom Bandung. Semua Acara bersifat <strong>GRATIS</strong></p>\n<p><br />Acara ini akan seru karena selama 2 hari tersebut akan ramai "full" seminar dan pelatihan. Berikut agenda acaranya :</p>\n<p><br />Tanggal : 28/04/2012</p>\n<p>Date/Time<span> </span>Event</p>\n<p>11:00 am - 1:00 pm<span> </span>Seminar Nasional: Perkembangan TIK dan Dampaknya bagi Masyarakat Indonesia&nbsp;Auditorium, Bandung Jawa Barat<br />2:00 pm - 4:00 pm<span> </span>Pemberdayaan Desa Melalui TIK&nbsp;Kelas B, Bandung Jawa Barat<br />2:00 pm - 4:00 pm<span> </span>Strategi Migrasi Open Source untuk Kantor/Sekolah&nbsp;Kelas A, Bandung Jawa Barat<br />2:00 pm - 4:00 pm<span> </span>TIK untuk Dunia Pendidikan&nbsp;Kelas D, Bandung Jawa Barat<br />2:00 pm - 4:00 pm<span> </span>Trend &amp; Peluang Game Developer&nbsp;Kelas C, Bandung Jawa Barat<br />2:00 pm - 5:00 pm<span> </span>Workshop: Open BTS, Teknologi Telekomunikasi Terbuka&nbsp;Auditorium, Bandung Jawa Barat<br />4:00 pm - 9:00 pm<span> </span>MUNAS RELAWAN TIK&nbsp;Kelas A, Bandung Jawa Barat<br />9:00 am - 12:00 pm<span> </span>Berbagi Informasi lewat Twitter&nbsp;Kelas C, Bandung Jawa Barat</p>\n<p><br />Tanggal : 29/04/2012</p>\n<p>Date/Time<span> </span>Event</p>\n<p>9:00 am - 12:00 pm<span> </span>Mencari Untung Lewat Blog&nbsp;Kelas A, Bandung Jawa Barat<br />9:00 am - 12:00 pm<span> </span>Pengembangan Aplikasi Android&nbsp;Kelas B, Bandung Jawa Barat<br />9:00 am - 12:00 pm<span> </span>Sosialisasi